3 Hours Ago According to Aruwan, the state government will issue a comprehensive statement “as soon as possible”. The statement read, “The Kaduna State Government is receiving security reports of kidnapping of some pupils and teachers in a primary school located in Rema, Birnin Gwari local government area. “According to preliminary reports, the incident occurred at an LEA Primary School in the LGA.”